textBox.richText: Today we managed to meet one of the world biggest tennis stars - Maria Sharapova.We were pretty lucky that she was looking for a little bit of a warm up before her hit out at the US Open later today. They had a radar gun to clock the speed of our serves. Flick reached 45 miles per hour and I wasn’t far off the pace with a 88 miles per hour. The bloke told me that a number of my serves were too quick for the radar. I was pretty impressed about that! And before you ask let’s not talk about accuracy!
